&lt;h2 id=&#34;Usage&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#Usage&#34; class=&#34;headerlink&#34; title=&#34;Usage&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;Usage&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;After installing the plugin, all image urls will be converted to CDN urls automatically. For example, the origin markdown file is&lt;/p&gt;

